I know you're doing this for our own good.

00:20:52.440 --> 00:20:53.480
If this path doesn't work,

00:20:55.480 --> 00:20:56.720
we'll just think of another way.

00:20:58.720 --> 00:20:59.720
We can always find another path.

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:01.240
But...

00:21:02.000 --> 00:21:03.519
Xiaocan doesn't have time to wait.

00:21:09.960 --> 00:21:10.279
It's okay.

00:21:13.359 --> 00:21:14.400
Xiaocan...

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:20.440
