If I give my Life Energy to you,

00:22:35.039 --> 00:22:36.240
will you give me the money?

00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:39.079
Do we go to the bank?

00:22:39.599 --> 00:22:40.200
Or do we do it here?

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:49.119
Kiddo.

00:22:50.000 --> 00:22:51.200
Auntie was lying to you.

00:22:51.559 --> 00:22:52.480
There's no such thing.

00:22:52.839 --> 00:22:53.799
It's getting late.

00:22:54.839 --> 00:22:55.799
Hurry home and rest.

00:22:58.960 --> 00:22:59.839
I'm serious.

00:23:03.839 --> 00:23:04.519
With the money,

00:23:05.200 --> 00:23:06.559
my parents won't have to work,

00:23:06.920 --> 00:23:07.720
and they can keep me company.

00:23:12.720 --> 00:23:13.759
But have you thought about it?

00:23:15.039 --> 00:23:16.359
If you leave this world early,

00:23:16.359 --> 00:23:17.240
what will your parents do?

00:23:19.920 --> 00:23:21.799
Do you know how sad and heartbroken they'll be?

00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:23.440
You living a good life,

00:23:23.599 --> 00:23:24.960
spending your life happily and safely,

00:23:25.279 --> 00:23:26.960
is what they want to see, you know?

00:23:54.119 --> 00:23:55.279
Little one, I'm sorry.

